BESTCOM INFOTECH said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 8.39% to NT$786,807,000 from NT$858,908,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales            786,807          858,908    
YOY%              -8.39%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           3,247,070        3,410,715   
YOY%              -4.80% 
=================================================================
 